summary: An Ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 3014 for the improvement of Sixtieth Avenue Southwest, from the south margin of West Stevens Street to the south margin of West Spokane Street, under Ordinance No. 36279, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
